about.projectDescription: Boutique 23 in Al Jaddaf, delivers an upscale urban lifestyle within its 23-storey tower. Located in a lively district, it seamlessly blends luxury amenities with the convenience of nearby cultural landmarks, premium sports facilities, and luxury hotels, making it an ideal choice for refined city living. The development offers both residential and office spaces, thoughtfully designed with modern aesthetics and functionality to ensure a luxurious and comfortable environment.

amenities.text: Boutique 23 offers residents an impressive array of amenities aimed at elevating their living experience. These include a refreshing swimming pool, a state-of-the-art gym, ample underground and podium parking, and a tranquil courtyard for relaxation. Additionally, on-site retail outlets provide convenient shopping and dining options, contributing to a vibrant and self-sufficient community.

content.title: Swimming pool
content.text: Surrounded by stylish lounge areas, the pool offers a serene escape from the urban hustle.

content.title: Fitness Centre
content.text: The fitness center boasts modern equipment for both casual exercisers and fitness enthusiasts.

content.title: Landscaped Area
content.text: The serene courtyard is a highlight within the development, providing a serene atmosphere.

content.title: Kids’ playground
content.text: The kids’ playground is a vibrant, well-designed space equipped with interactive play structures.

content.title: Covered parking
content.text: The four-level underground parking and podium parking offer ample spaces for residents.

content.title: Retail shops
content.text: The retail spaces provide diverse shopping and dining options, enriching the lifestyle experience.
Our installment schemas are devoid of any latent charges or unanticipated costs.
A 4% DLD (Dubai Land Department) fee applies to all real estate transactions in Dubai and must be paid in addition to the property's purchase price.

Since its inception in 2007, LMD has been crafting transformative experiences through thriving communities and integrated destinations. The company boasts a successful selection of projects, spanning first and second homes, as well as iconic mixed-use developments with a strong foothold in Dubai, Spain and Greece.
